<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Belajar Git & Branching</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f172a;
      --bg-soft: #111827;
      --accent: #38bdf8;
      --accent-soft: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.09);
      --text-main: #e5e7eb;
      --text-muted: #9ca3af;
      --border-soft: #1f2937;
      --danger: #f97373;
      --success: #4ade80;
      --radius-lg: 14px;
      --radius-xl: 18px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
        sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1e293b 0, #020617 55%);
      color: var(--text-main);
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 24px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 900px;
    }

    .card {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #020617, #020617, #020617);
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      box-shadow:
        0 18px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7),
        0 0 0 1px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9) inset;
      padding: 28px 24px 24px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    }

    header {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .logo-pill {
      width: 52px;
      height: 52px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, #38bdf8, #0ea5e9);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      box-shadow:
        0 0 0 4px rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.3),
        0 10px 30px rgba(8, 47, 73, 0.9);
    }

    .logo-pill span {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #e0f2fe;
    }

    .title-block h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .badge {
      font-size: 11px;
      padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.5);
      color: var(--text-muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .title-block p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 2.1fr) minmax(0, 1.6fr);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      body {
        padding: 16px;
      }
      .card {
        padding: 20px 16px 18px;
      }
    }

    .panel {
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #0b1220 0, #020617 65%);
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      padding: 14px 14px 12px;
    }

    .panel-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .panel-title {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .dots {
      display: flex;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .dot {
      width: 7px;
      height: 7px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #4b5563;
    }

    .dot:nth-child(1) {
      background: #f97373;
    }
    .dot:nth-child(2) {
      background: #facc15;
    }
    .dot:nth-child(3) {
      background: #4ade80;
    }

    .terminal {
      background: #020617;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid #111827;
      font-family: "JetBrains Mono", ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo,
        Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      padding: 10px 12px 8px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      line-height: 1.5;
      max-height: 240px;
      overflow: auto;
    }

    .prompt {
      color: #38bdf8;
    }

    .cmd {
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    .comment {
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .accent-line {
      border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
      padding-left: 10px;
      margin: 4px 0 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    ul {
      margin-left: 18px;
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    li + li {
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .pill-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .pill {
      font-size: 11px;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(45, 212, 191, 0.35);
      color: #a5f3fc;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .checklist {
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .check-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-top: 4px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .check-icon {
      width: 14px;
      margin-top: 2px;
      color: var(--success);
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 14px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      padding-top: 10px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .tag-main {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="card">
      <header>
        <div class="logo-pill">
          <span>git</span>
        </div>
        <div class="title-block">
          <h1>
            Belajar Git & Branching
            <span class="badge">Latihan di lokal dulu</span>
          </h1>
          <p>
            Halaman ini cuma buat latihan:
            <span class="tag-main">branch, commit, push, merge</span>.
            Aman diutak-atik sesuka hati.
          </p>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="grid">
        <!-- Panel kiri: terminal simulasi -->
        <section class="panel">
          <div class="panel-header">
            <span class="panel-title">Simulasi Terminal</span>
            <div class="dots">
              <span class="dot"></span>
              <span class="dot"></span>
              <span class="dot"></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accent-line">
            Workflow standar:
            <strong>edit â†’ add â†’ commit â†’ push</strong>.
          </div>
          <div class="terminal">
            <div>
              <span class="prompt">bagus@laptop</span>:<span class="cmd">~/git/html-basic</span>$ 
              <span class="cmd">git status</span>
            </div>
            <div class="comment">On branch branch-latihan</div>
            <div class="comment">nothing to commit, working tree clean</div>
            <br />

            <div>
              <span class="prompt">bagus@laptop</span>:<span class="cmd">~/git/html-basic</span>$ 
              <span class="cmd"># 1. Edit file HTML ini</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="prompt">bagus@laptop</span>:<span class="cmd">~/git/html-basic</span>$ 
              <span class="cmd">git add index.html</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="prompt">bagus@laptop</span>:<span class="cmd">~/git/html-basic</span>$ 
              <span class="cmd">git commit -m "Update tampilan halaman latihan"</span>
            </div>
            <div class="comment">[branch-latihan abc1234] Update tampilan halaman latihan</div>
            <div class="comment"> 1 file changed, 10 insertions(+)</div>
            <br />

            <div>
              <span class="prompt">bagus@laptop</span>:<span class="cmd">~/git/html-basic</span>$ 
              <span class="cmd">git push</span>
            </div>
            <div class="comment">
              â†’ Perubahan terkirim ke remote (GitHub) untuk branch ini.
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Panel kanan: ringkasan & checklist -->
        <section class="panel">
          <div class="panel-header">
            <span class="panel-title">Ringkasan Latihan</span>
            <div class="dots">
              <span class="dot"></span>
              <span class="dot"></span>
              <span class="dot"></span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="section-title">Tujuan Halaman</div>
            <p class="accent-line">
              Halaman ini dipakai untuk:
              <strong>latihan Git di lokal</strong> sebelum benar-benar
              kolaborasi pakai akun kantor.
            </p>

            <ul>
              <li>Coba bikin branch baru, misalnya: <code>branch-latihan</code></li>
              <li>Edit isi paragraf, judul, atau checklist di bawah.</li>
              <li>Commit perubahan, lalu push ke branch tersebut.</li>
              <li>Kalau sudah pede, baru merge ke <code>main</code>.</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="pill-row">
              <span class="pill">git switch -c branch-latihan</span>
              <span class="pill">git status</span>
              <span class="pill">git add index.html</span>
              <span class="pill">git commit -m "..."</span>
              <span class="pill">git push</span>
            </div>

            <div class="section-title" style="margin-top: 12px;">
              Checklist yang bisa kamu coba
            </div>
            <div class="checklist">
              <div class="check-item">
                <span class="check-icon">âœ”</span>
                <span>Buat <strong>branch baru</strong> khusus untuk halaman ini.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="check-item">
                <span class="check-icon">âœ”</span>
                <span>
                  Ubah sedikit teks di atas, commit dengan pesan yang
                  <em>jelas</em>.
                </span>
              </div>
              <div class="check-item">
                <span class="check-icon">âœ”</span>
                <span>
                  Push branch tersebut ke GitHub, lihat perbedaan di tab
                  <strong>Branches</strong>.
                </span>
              </div>
              <div class="check-item">
                <span class="check-icon">âœ”</span>
                <span>
                  Setelah paham, coba buat <strong>Pull Request</strong> dari
                  branch latihan ke <code>main</code>.
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      <footer>
        <span>Made for: latihan Git lokal & cabang-cabangan ðŸ™ƒ</span>
        <span>Step berikutnya: coba kolaborasi pakai akun kantor.</span>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

